  "title": "Horticulturist (Landscape)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li><strong>Salary range: $2000 - $2500</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Working hours: 8am – 5pm (Monday – Friday), 8am – 12pm (Saturday)</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Location: Various Location in Singapore</strong></li>\n  <li><strong>Well Established Landscape Company</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in the planting, cultivation, and maintenance of trees, shrubs, flowers, and turf.</li>\n  <li>Conduct watering, pruning, fertilizing, pest and disease control, and general plant care.</li>\n  <li>Help with landscape design implementation and upkeep of gardens or green areas.</li>\n  <li>Monitor plant health and report any issues to senior horticulturists or supervisors.</li>\n  <li>Support nursery operations — propagation, potting, soil mixing, and plant tagging.</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and safety in the work area and equipment used.</li>\n  <li>Keep simple records of plant growth, maintenance activities, and material usage.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirement</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Horticulture / Landscape Architecture or related field.</li>\n  <li><strong>No experience is required as training provided</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li>\n  <li>Current and Expected salary</li>\n  <li>Reason for leaving</li>\n  <li>Date of availability</li>\n  <li>Education background</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)</p>\n<p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
